  "prompt": "What will be the PSU cut off for the all categories?",
  "response": "The cut-off scores for Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs) vary each year based on factors such as the number of applicants, the difficulty level of the exam, and the number of vacancies available. These cut-offs are determined after the examination results are announced and can differ across different PSUs and job roles.\n\nFor accurate and updated cut-off details, you should refer to the official announcements from the respective PSUs or related examination conducting bodies once the results and subsequent selection processes are underway. Consider checking the official websites of the PSUs you\u2019re interested in or looking for notifications released by them for the most precise information.",
